Recommendations

The trends shows that accidents are extremely seasonal, and you can almost predict them. Predictability ensures we can put measures in place to prevent occurrences in the time, season, and weather conditions notable with high rate of accidents and high severity accidents. Measures may include:

1. Road signs and warnings displayed in strategic places or during these notable periods

2. Increased Law Enforcement presence during these notable periods
